<chapter condition="TITLE=Lending Services" id="LN_Main" role="TOPIC">
  <title>Lending Services</title>

  <para role="TEXT">The Lending Services menu on the toolbar, provides
  facilities to manage loans, document tracking and bills through the
  <xi:include href="../entities_en.xml" xpointer="ent_appli"
  xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" />.</para>

 <note>
      <para role="TEXT">The availability of the Lending Services menu and its functions is
      dependent on the permissions assigned to the user. Only those functions
      the user is authorised to use, will be displayed.</para>
    </note>

  <para role="TEXT">The menu for this module has the following groups of
  functions.</para> <para role="TEXT">
      <variablelist>
        <varlistentry>
          <term>
            <guimenuitem moreinfo="none">Loan</guimenuitem>
          </term>

          <listitem>
            <para role="TEXT">All functions relating to Loans, for example, Loan
            Maintenance, Loan Increase, Loan Payments, and so on.</para>
          </listitem>
        </varlistentry>

        <varlistentry>
          <term>
            <guimenuitem moreinfo="none">Document Tracking</guimenuitem>
          </term>

          <listitem>
            <para role="TEXT">A list of Pending Compliance documents.</para>
          </listitem>
        </varlistentry>

        <varlistentry>
          <term>
            <guimenuitem moreinfo="none">Bill</guimenuitem>
          </term>

          <listitem>
            <para role="TEXT">A list of the last nine pending bills.</para>
          </listitem>
        </varlistentry>
      </variablelist>
    </para>

  <xi:include href="FCC_user_client_en.loan.xml" xpointer="LN"
              xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" />

